Local-only no-send DTS v2 preview.

Do not send this patch as-is. It is a coordination artifact for the A733 /
Radxa Cubie A7S local-work-only workflow. It exists to preview the narrow
UART0 pinctrl source movement requested by maintainer feedback and to support
future static validation. It is not runtime proof, not b4 metadata, not a
public branch, and not approval to mutate hardware.

Expected local checks before any future use:

- `git apply --check` against the selected clean source tree
- `git diff --check` after applying in a temporary full tree
- targeted DTB build
- `CHECK_DTBS=y` targeted DTB build
- `scripts/checkpatch.pl --strict`
- `scripts/get_maintainer.pl`

Runtime proof remains queued-only under A733-BATCH-002. Communications remain
held under A733-COMM-002 and A733-COMM-003.

